title: Alpha Leader
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

Any friendly unit within 12" of [[Old One Eye]] can choose to use [[Old One Eye]]’s Leadership for any Morale or Leadership tests they are required to make. In addition, friendly [[Carnifex]] broods treat [[Old One Eye]] as though it were an [[Independent Character]] and [[Old One Eye]] considers friendly [[Carnifex]]es to be [[Infantry]] for the purposes of joining and leaving units.